body:
Thanks for the reviews.

The Windows CMake test [failed](https://ci.tensorflow.org/job/tensorflow-pr-win-cmake-py/896/consoleFull), but that looks like an unrelated race condition in the [input_test.py](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/python/training/input_test.py#L987). A vague look seems like ``all_a`` and ``seen_b`` should be getting checked rather than ``which_a`` and ``which_b``, [possibly](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/python/training/input_test.py#L979).
